OL,3,CWorld breaks 1.5C warming limit for
OL,4,Cfirst time over a year long period
OL,6,FThe 1.5C limit was a target of the
OL,7,FParis Agreement made in 2015, though
OL,8,Fcontinued emissions since then have
OL,9,Fmade it increasingly difficult to
OL,10,Fachieve
OL,12,FGlobal warming has exceeded 1.5C
OL,13,Fwarming limit across an entire year
OL,14,Ffor the first time, according to the
OL,15,FEuropean Union's climate service.
OL,17,FThe global mean temperature for the
OL,18,Fpast twelve months, between February
OL,19,F2023 and January 2024, was 1.52C above
OL,20,Fthe 1850-1900 pre-industrial average.
