OL,3,CWorld breaks 1.5C warming limit for
OL,4,Cfirst time over a year long period
OL,6,FThe 1.5C limit was a key target of the
OL,7,FParis Agreement made in 2015, though
OL,8,Fcontinued emissions since then have
OL,9,Fmade it increasingly difficult to
OL,10,Fachieve.
OL,12,FThis temperature rise does not mean
OL,13,Fthe agreement has failed - the limit
OL,14,Fwill only be broken if it becomes the
OL,15,Faverage for around 20 years, so any
OL,16,Findividual year above that would not
OL,17,Fmean a failure.
