OL,3,CWorld breaks 1.5C warming limit for
OL,4,Cfirst time over a year long period
OL,6,FThe current level of warming is
OL,7,Festimated to be around 1.3C above pre-
OL,8,Findustrial levels, the Met Office said
OL,9,Fin January.
OL,11,FIt comes as January 2024 was the
OL,12,Fwarmest January on record globally.
OL,14,FThe month saw an average ERA5 surface
OL,15,Fair temperature of 13.14C - 0.70C
OL,16,Fabove the 1991-2020 average for
OL,17,FJanuary.
OL,19,FIt was 0.12C above the temperature of
OL,20,Fthe previous warmest first month of
OL,21,Fthe year, in 2020.
