OL,3,CWorld breaks 1.5C warming limit for
OL,4,Cfirst time over a year long period
OL,6,FThe information was compiled by
OL,7,FCopernicus, a component of the
OL,8,FEuropean Union's space programme which
OL,9,Fmonitors six key topics - atmosphere,
OL,10,Fmarine, land, climate change, security
OL,11,Fand emergency.
OL,13,FEuropean temperatures varied in
OL,14,FJanuary 2024 from much below the 1991-
OL,15,F2020 average over the Nordic countries
OL,16,Fto much above average over the south
OL,17,Fof the continent.
